The paper deals with the problem of evacuating a dynamic path network, which involves optimizing the flow of evacuees through a network with capacity constraints. This problem is closely related to topics in computer science such as algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
